          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Charcoal filter replacement</div><div class="repair-desc">Smell control, 3-6 month interval</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$40&ndash;$80</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ filter ($25&ndash;$50)</div></td>
            <td>Filter replacement plus drum interior wipe-down. Operator-level maintenance many LA households skip.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Drive gear replacement</div><div class="repair-desc">Loud grinding, ram won&rsquo;t fully extend</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$280&ndash;$440</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ gear set ($60&ndash;$140)</div></td>
            <td>Year 8-11 typical wear. Drive gear teeth strip from forced operation against jam. Compactor extraction from cabinet, gear replacement, lubrication, reinstall.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Ram motor replacement</div><div class="repair-desc">Hum but no compaction, motor burned out</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$380&ndash;$540</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ motor ($120&ndash;$240)</div></td>
            <td>Year 10-13 typical on built-in. Highest single-component cost. Compactor extraction, motor replacement, drive coupling check, reinstall.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Drum bearing service</div><div class="repair-desc">Drum binding or noisy during cycle</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$220&ndash;$340</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ bearing ($45&ndash;$80)</div></td>
            <td>Year 7-10 typical. Drum bearing replacement, drum trueness check, lubrication of pivot points.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Compactor jam clearing</div><div class="repair-desc">Oversized item or overfill stopping ram mid-cycle</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$140&ndash;$220</div><div class="price-parts-note">Usually no parts</div></td>
            <td>Manual reset, jam removal, ram return-to-home test. Operator education on bag capacity. Some calls resolve at $89 diagnostic + visit.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Control board replacement</div><div class="repair-desc">Multiple switches unresponsive, electronic models</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$280&ndash;$440</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ board ($120&ndash;$220)</div></td>
            <td>Premium electronic-control models (KitchenAid Architect Series II) at year 10-13. Less common than mechanical-control.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Diagnostic fee</div><div class="repair-desc">Full diagnosis incl. ram, switch, gear, seal</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$89</div><div class="price-parts-note">Applied to repair</div></td>
            <td>Includes ram motor function test, switch operation test, drive gear inspection, drum seal check.</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p class="table-note"><strong>All prices are labor only.</strong> Parts quoted separately. Quote before we start; invoice matches the quote. 90-day warranty on parts and labor.</p>
  </div>
</section>
